txt.en: 'These are flawless! I thank you adventurer.\n\n'I will make some fine arrows with these.'
Paguri in Ub Nishir has asked you to gather feathers from birds in Urash Dâr so that she can replenish her stock of arrows.
Bring the pristine feathers back to Paguri in Ub Nishir.

Paguri in Ub Nashir has asked you to gather feathers from nearby birds so that she can replenish her stock of arrows.

'Ah, an adventurer. Could I trouble you for some help?

'I am the fletcher here and I am working to build our supply of arrows. We will need all that we can get if we mean to retake Maurûsh.

'If you happen upon any feathers from the creatures here in Urash Dâr, I would be glad to take them off your hands. I do not have the time myself to track them down with the work that must be done.

'Only ones remaining in pristine condition will suffice.'
